# Model training and export

Download a current checkpoint and pipeline.config from the official TF2 Detection Model Zoo. Configure the number of classes, record paths, label map, batch size, fine-tune checkpoint, and train steps.

Run the installed Model Garden commands documented in README.md. Do not use the copied 2022 model_main_tf2.py and exporter scripts for new training; use the installed scripts in third_party/models/research/object_detection instead.
